&lt;p&gt;As the Market Operations Director (MOD), you will serve as the senior operational leader responsible for the performance, growth, and clinical integrity of Guidelight Health&#39;s clinics across Colorado. Reporting directly to the Chief Operating Officer, you will partner with site-level Executive Directors and clinical leadership to drive a unified vision, one where exceptional patient outcomes and sustainable business performance go hand in hand.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a high-impact, highly visible role for a leader who thrives at the intersection of clinical excellence, operational strategy, and team development. You will be accountable for market-level KPIs spanning access, clinical outcomes, financial performance, and team engagement, and you will lead with both the analytical rigor to drive results and the human-centered approach to build a culture people are proud to be part of. If you are energized by building things, developing people, and driving growth in a fast-paced, high-growth environment, this role is for you.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
